text.tspan: Median monthly per capita expenditure around 1985 versus Median
Countries for which the per capita consumption expenditure is not available income is shown instead. All measures are
adjusted for price differences over time (expressed in 2011 prices) and are adjusted for price differences between countries
(expressed in international dollars). Since the data is not available annually it has to be shown in a range around the two years
(the exact year is visible on hover).
